Awsome awsome awsome, thank you guys for the wonderful delicious food, great service, great food as always... I'll be back for more 👍👍👍
The branch I have visited the most. Love the experience every time that I visit. Located in a beautiful area. Excellent meals and service.
A nice place to go for Indian/Pakistani "South East Asian" food with a huge variety of curries to rice to kebabs to pizza etc. And a special buffett on every Wednesday from 6pm....

This Indian restaurant is a hidden gem in Gold Coast. I felt hungry and looked for food in google map. I found this and thought it was a small food shop. Surprisingly when I reached there, it was not but a proper Indian restaurant. I ordered Prawn curry and Nan bread take away.  Both of them just tasted sooooo good! Freshie prawns and well-textured bread. And most importantly they wrapped the food with tin foil, so that I could serve them hot and the bread was 100% free of condensed water even after 30 minutes drive before reaching home. Just perfect! ^^

result.name: Gold Coast Apartments

reviews.text:
Very much loving this apartment! It has bus shuttle everyday to go to many places. And my favourite place to go is Tuen Mun Mall :)
I love this place is because it has tranquil and quite environment, safe and very clean. It has a chinese restaurant outside near the lobby. Even though not really good taste but not bad for having lunch or dinner.
Apartment complex in a nice area. Well maintained but the complex is 15 to 20 years old. Rents are lower than Kowloon are but the place is far away from the Hong Kong business areas
Reasonable services, plenty of space and facilities even has a beach next to it. You find also generous public parking right outside the hotel,  you don't find that often in HK.
Best service ever offered with morning newspaper delivered daily in the room.

Very nice venue and setup. Needs a bit more attention to cleaning and general maintenance.  Could have been a better venue. Bed was way too hard.  They tried to soften with a pillow top but they need tk change the mattresses instead :)
